OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FThe pressure to find school places in
OL,7,FCornwall for children with special
OL,8,Feducation needs has left 73 children
OL,9,Fwith no idea where which school they
OL,10,Fwill be attending this September.
OL,12,FIn February Cornwall Council had a
OL,13,Flegal deadline to tell families where
OL,14,Ftheir primary school children will go
OL,15,Fnext but there have been difficulties
OL,16,Ffinding specialist places for SEN
OL,17,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
