OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FThe caseload of children with
OL,7,FEducational Health and Care Plans in
OL,8,FCornwall has risen sharply, from 4,700
OL,9,Fin Oct 2024 to 5,600 to date.
OL,11,FCornwall is one of the lowest funded
OL,12,Flocal authorities in the country for
OL,13,Feducation and combined with poverty
OL,14,Frates leaves a disproportionate effect
OL,15,Fchildren with special educational
OL,16,Fneeds.
OL,18,FJoseph Adams is one of those children
OL,19,Fwaiting for his secondary school place.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
