FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FThe 11-year-old from Liskeard has
OL,7,Fautism and needs additional support
OL,8,Fduring the school day.
OL,10,FHe has written a letter of complaint
OL,11,Fto Cornwall Council telling them he
OL,12,Ffeels "feel scared and anxious and
OL,13,Fsometimes sick" after delays and
OL,14,Funcertainty over his future school
OL,15,Fplace.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FHe said: "I'm stressed, pressured and
OL,7,Fall those other negative emotions
OL,8,Fbecause everyone one can talk about
OL,9,Fthat where they are going to secondary
OL,10,Fschool. I can't because I don't know
OL,11,Fit yet. So I don't really put much
OL,12,Ftrust of the council right now."
OL,14,FJoseph's family want him to attend the
OL,15,Fnearest school, Liskeard School and
OL,16,FCommunity College, but have been told
OL,17,FSEN places there are full. He is still
OL,18,Fbeing kept waiting for a SEN placement
OL,19,Fat an alternative school.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FHis Grandad Mike Adams has helped
OL,7,FJoseph record musical videos to appeal
OL,8,Fto Cornwall Council to look again at
OL,9,Ffinding room for him at Liskeard.
OL,11,FMr Adams said: "It's very upsetting,
OL,12,Fyou want to be able to help, but you
OL,13,Ffeel useless because you can't do
OL,14,Fanything."
OL,16,F"So (Joseph) did a couple of videos to
OL,17,Ftry to just make the council to see
OL,18,Fthat he's a lovely little boy and he's
OL,19,Fnot a name on a piece of paper and he
OL,20,Fdeserves better."
OL,26,@xD@EpmxD@Lpn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FThe Adams' family have been told to
OL,7,Fexpect an update about Joseph's school
OL,8,Fplacement by June but they have have
OL,9,Falready put in a formal complaint
OL,10,Fabout the way his case has been
OL,11,Fhandled.
OL,13,FThe charity Contact, who support
OL,14,Ffamilies with disabled children, says
OL,15,Flack of certainty in the lead up to
OL,16,Fthe new school year and travelling
OL,17,Flong distances can be difficult for
OL,18,FSEN children to manage.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FAngie Fenn, Head of Information and
OL,7,FAdvice at Contact says it's really
OL,8,Fimportant child arrive at school in
OL,9,F"the best frame of mind so that they
OL,10,Fcan be ready to learn and be involved
OL,11,Fin the school day.
OL,13,F"Long distances can be tiring. They
OL,14,Fcan also be a challenging environment
OL,15,Fif it's transport where there's
OL,16,Fmultiple children being transferred.
OL,17,FThey may have early start times and
OL,18,Flater drop offs."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FCouncillor Hilary Frank is Cornwall's
OL,7,Fcabinet member for children, families
OL,8,Fand schools.
OL,10,FShe says there's been a "huge rise in
OL,11,Fdemand" with 30% more families asking
OL,12,Ffor an ECHP assessment. But it is "not
OL,13,Fgood enough" how long families are
OL,14,Fbeing kept waiting for a confirmed
OL,15,Fsecondary school place.
OL,17,F"My heart goes out to them. It's
OL,18,Freally not acceptable that they are
OL,19,Fwaiting like this."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
