OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FCornwall Council has already opened
OL,7,Fadditional settings for children with
OL,8,Fspecialist needs including a social
OL,9,Femotional mental health (SEMH) primary
OL,10,Fschool at Cury, Bosvena School in
OL,11,FBodmin, Redruth Secondary School and
OL,12,Fextensions Doubletrees and Pencalenick
OL,13,Fand adding satellites to our other
OL,14,Fspecial schools Nancealverne
OL,15,F(satellite is Roscadgill), Curnow
OL,16,F(satellite is Karder).
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
