FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FRecently the Government has allocated
OL,7,F#9.19 million in funding for Cornwall
OL,8,FCouncil to spend on building more
OL,9,Fschool places for higher needs
OL,10,Fchildren for 2026`27.
OL,12,FIt aims for more children like Joseph
OL,13,Fto be taught within mainstream
OL,14,Fsettings.
OL,16,FHowever this takes time as schools
OL,17,Fhold public consultations and then
OL,18,Fwait for Department for Education to
OL,19,Fapprove new building works.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
