FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776760723
OL,3,C73 children still waiting for SEN
OL,4,Csecondary school place in Cornwall
OL,6,FCornwall Council say they hope to have
OL,7,F80 places ready for the upcoming
OL,8,Fschool year, giving all 73 children
OL,9,Fcurrently waiting a place to attend,
OL,10,Fand 200 places in the near future.
OL,12,FUntil then, families are being kept
OL,13,Fwaiting to see if what they are
OL,14,Foffered is going to be suitable for
OL,15,Ftheir children.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
